slm.pl: The raw log monitoring program

ssm.pl: A companion program to slm to check process status,
        hosts, File Systems, and FDFs

slm.config: sample configuration file for slm

ssm.config: sample configuration file for ssm

install.pl: the real installation script (usually executed by install.sh)

install.sh: installation script 

IW_support.pl: General support routine library for InforWatcher

slm.conf.man: the configuration man page

slm.prog.man: the program man page

README: a brief synopsis of the program

CONTENTS:  this file

